Long field headland mode

Long field headland mode #2577 and #2333
Course for long and narrow fields. Under the hood it generates headland rows only until they cover the entire field, but on the short edge of the field every row except the outermost one has zero offset.
Works fine for rectangular fields, may not be very pretty for odd shaped ones but there this mode doesn't really make sense anyway.
